---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import avatar from "../assets/avatar.jpg";

const url = new URL(Astro.url);
const avatarParameter = url.searchParams.get("avatar");
---

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto my-10 bg-white p-8 rounded-lg">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-8 gap-4">
    <div class="col-span-6">
      <section>
        <div class="text-2xl font-semibold">
          Stanislav Strugovshchikov (Stas)
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm">Full-Stack Developer</div>
        <div class="text-sm">Orlando, Florida, 🇺🇸 United States</div>
      </section>

      <section class="mt-2">
        <h2 class="font-semibold">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-sm mt-1">📞 +1 (786) 325 4891</p>
        <p class="text-sm mt-1">✉️ stanislav.stru@gmail.com</p>
        <div class="flex gap-3 divide-x divide-gray-500 mt-1 text-sm">
          <span class="pr-3">
            🔗 <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/strugovshchikov"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-blue-600">LinkedIn</a
            >
          </span>
          <span>
            🔗 <a
              href="https://github.com/stanislavstru"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-blue-600">GitHub</a
            >
          </span>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    {
      avatarParameter && (
        <div class="col-span-2">
          <Image
            src={avatar}
            alt="Stanislav Strugovshchikov"
            class="rounded-lg"
          />
        </div>
      )
    }
  </div>

  <section class="mt-4">
    <h2 class="text font-semibold">Summary</h2>
    <p class="ml-3 mt-1 text-sm">
      Full-Stack Developer with over 10 years of experience in web application
      development, AI assistant integration, and scalable front-end and back-end
      solutions. Expertise in JavaScript, Node.js, React, Next.js, PHP, and
      microfrontend architectures. Strong background in building AI-powered
      applications, integrating LLM-based solutions, and developing intelligent
      automation tools. Successfully developed multiple social networks and
      complex platforms used by over 3,000 users.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-4">
    <h2 class="font-semibold">Skills</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-1 text-sm">
      <li>
        <strong>Frontend:</strong> TypeScript, React, Next.js, Astro.js, Redux, TailwindCSS
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Mobile:</strong> React Native, Ionic, Capacitor, Responsive Layout
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js, Express, NestJS, PHP (Yii2, Symfony)
      </li>
      <li><strong>Databases:</strong> PostgreSQL, MongoDB, MySQL</li>
      <li>
        <strong>DevOps & Tools:</strong> Docker, AWS, Firebase, Vercel, Jenkins
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>AI & Integrations:</strong> OpenAI API, ChatGPT, Stripe API
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Other:</strong> Microservices, NX, GraphQL, REST API, WebSockets,
        Wordpress
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-4">
    <h2 class="font-semibold">Experience</h2>

    <div class="ml-3 mt-1 text-sm">
      <div class="mt-2">
        <a href="https://www.criya.co/" target="_blank"
          ><h3 class="text-md font-bold">Criya | Full Stack Engineer</h3></a
        >
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          June 2022 - Present (2 years 9 months) | United States
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
          <li>
            The project was migrated from Ruby to Next.js, resulting in a 100%
            increase in performance and improved search engine rankings.
          </li>
          <li>
            Integrated LLM mechanisms and AI Agent workflows to enable
            end-to-end personalized AI-driven marketing campaigns in under 60
            seconds
          </li>
          <li>
            Implemented 15 different third-party payment, analytics, auth
            integrations
          </li>
          <li>
            Designed a monorepo-based architecture with modular application
            separation. Established a reusable codebase, significantly improving
            project performance.
          </li>
          <li>
            Developed a style library that was later used for all new project
            integrations.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-3">
        <a href="https://dzsystems.ru/en/" target="_blank"
          ><h3 class="text-md font-bold">DZ Systems | Front End Lead</h3></a
        >

        <p class="text-gray-600">
          February 2021 - June 2022 (1 year 5 months) | Russia
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
          <li>
            Developed a social network for business professionals and
            implemented a WebSockets-based chat system for negotiation
            coordination, reducing the process to just 3 steps globally
          </li>
          <li>Built microservices architecture for high scalability.</li>
          <li>Localized the project into 5 languages.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-3">
        <a href="https://pro.myseldon.com/en/promo" target="_blank"
          ><h3 class="text-md font-bold">Seldon Pro | Software Engineer</h3></a
        >
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          January 2020 - February 2021 (1 year 2 months) | Russia
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
          <li>
            Migrated legacy projects from jQuery to Next.js, increasing
            efficiency by 200%.
          </li>
          <li>
            Established a configuration rule for collaboration between designers
            and front-end developers, tripling development speed.
          </li>
          <li>
            Introduced modern CSS frameworks to enhance styling and
            maintainability.
          </li>
          <li>
            Established seamless collaboration between C# developers and the
            Front-end team.
          </li>
          <li>
            Optimized PostgreSQL database performance by 37% without changing
            the number of queried parameters
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-3">
        <a href="https://mebelidomanet.ru/" target="_blank"
          ><h3 class="text-md font-bold">
            Mebelidomanet | Full-Stack Developer
          </h3></a
        >

        <p class="text-gray-600">
          April 2017 - May 2020 (3 years 2 months) | Russia
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc ml-6">
          <li>
            I have successfully developed several big marketplaces, including a
            market place in Russia, namely a core platform on which 147 online
            shops were built. Used Yii2.
          </li>
          <li>
            Collaborated on designing a structure for fast database queries.
          </li>
          <li>
            Our team worked on SEO optimization, resulting in over 43% of our
            websites ranking in the top 1-3 positions.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-4">
    <h2 class="font-semibold">Soft Skills</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mt-1 text-sm">
      <li>Effective communicator and a reliable team member.</li>
      <li>
        Analyzing technical challenges and implementing innovative solutions.
      </li>
      <li>
        Quick to learn new technologies and adjust to rapidly changing project
        requirements.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-4">
    <h2 class="font-semibold">Education</h2>
    <p class="ml-3 mt-1 text-sm">
      <strong>Russia, Nizhniy Novgorod, State Technical University</strong> (2007
      - 2012)
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-6 text-center text-sm">
    <p>🚀 Open to new opportunities and collaborations!</p>
  </section>
</div>
